data.title: List of Australian Americans
authors: Contributors to The JH Movie Collection's Official Wiki
data.meta_description: This is a list of notable Australian Americans, including both original immigrants who obtained American citizenship and their American descendants.
data.meta_site_name: The JH Movie Collection's Official Wiki
